body_html:
Hi all, thanks for the issue!
We may need to optimize some kernels that your models are using. We experienced up to 3x on models we optimized, but there are many ops that may still need extra attention :)

We are looking into this. To help us reproduce, could you provide the following:
(1) Which model are you running?
(2) What device/architecture are you running on?

Also, if possible could you provide your TFLite float and TFLite quantized model for reproducing? Feel free to direct email me.
